## Normal mode

### Delete

- until character (unsing the "till" motion): <kbd>d</kbd><kbd>t</kbd><kbd>CHAR</kbd>


## Visual mode



Open a file under cursor: 
<kbd>g</kbd><kbd>f</kbd>


